<p>The UPS is the unsung hero. It doesnâ€™t just â€œstay ready.â€ It actively conditions and stabilises the power every second of every day. And when the grid fails, the UPS is the thing that saves everything from crashing.</p>

<p><strong>Whatâ€™s inside a UPS room?</strong></p>
